NEWSMAKERS 
Kenneth W. Bray has been appointed to the newly created position of vice 
president, direct operations, for Zee Medical Inc., a subsidiary of McKesson 
Corp. He will supervise the operation of the company's eight regional sales 
centers in the United States and Canada. Previously, Bray was vice president, 
strategic planning, for several McKesson operations, including Zee Medical. 
Based in Irvine, Zee Medical supplies first-aid and safety services and 
products to businesses. 
